<div class="list_container">
<dl>

  <dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span>
  <a name="active" id="active"></a><strong>What is the use of the [ active / deactive ] option in the employees page ?
  </strong>
  <dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">
  	you can use this option , so that you dont delete the account of the employee when he leaves the company , so you keep all your data and never lose it , since that the employee is related to the projects tasks .  </dd></dt>
  <dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span>
  <a name="delemp" id="delemp"></a><strong>While am trying to delete one of the employee i got this error which tell me that i cant ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">
you cant delete an employee when he/she is related to a project task.</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="delDep" id="delDep"></a><strong>Am trying to delete one the departments but the system keep telling me that i cant do this operation ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">you cant delete a department while it has an employee assigned to it.</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="delCln" id="delCln"></a><strong>Am trying to delete one of the clients but the system keep telling me that i cant do that ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">you cant delete a clinet which has a project in the system</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="addProject" id="addProject"></a><strong>When i add a new project i cant see all the departments , why ?</strong> 
  <dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">you will only see the departments which has employees .</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="changeDep" id="changeDep"></a><strong>When i edit a project , why i cant change the departments ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">You cant change the project department once you add a task to the project.</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="newTask" id="newTask"></a><strong>When adding a new task , why i cant see all the employees ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">you will only see the active employees only.</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="newTask1" id="newTask1"></a><strong>When i add a new task , in the employee section i can see many employee not only the one related to the project department ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">The system will get you not only the employee inside this department , but also all the employees inside the branch sub departments.</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="gantt1" id="gantt1"></a><strong>When i try to see the gantt chart , i got this error which says permission error ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">Check if you give the cache directory the permission to read and write , which is 775 or 777 in linux servers.</dd></dt>
<dt class="odd" style="padding:5px 2px 0px 5px;"><span style="float:right"><a href="#top">TOP</a></span><a name="gantt2" id="gantt2"></a><strong>When i try to see the gantt chart , i always see a different one ( old chart ) ?</strong>
<dd style="margin-bottom:20px;">This error related to the internet browser cache , try to delete the cache or hit CTL+F5 .</dd></dt>
</dl></div>
